<br>
The image of a dark, mysterious profile in the background quietly chanting his spell and unleashing it with devestating results on his hapless victim is so very intriguing.  Also, playing on Sullon Zek is a breath of fresh air.  I've met some surprisingly kind people there, which is a nice change of pace from the other PvP servers I've encountered in the past (namely Rallos Zek).  I also love playing games with the difficulty level cranked up, and as I figure it, playing as a newbie wizard with no twink gear on the good team on sullon is about as hard as I'm going to get....well....aside from being a gnome, of course.  They're just gimped.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=swordshaman>SwordShaman</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.uwplatt.edu/~tkd/pics/traveler" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/6/03 2:37:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25246.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.uwplatt.edu/~tkd/pics/traveler.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What makes your wizard fun to play?</span><hr size=1> And may I ask what 'spell shield' is?  Must be a new spell introduced after I quit a good while back.  Also, what ways are there beyond our familiar and harvest line to increase our mana regen?  I've heard of 'flowing thought' focus effect items, though I haven't seen one for sale in the bazaar yet.  I'm sure they're quite pricey and rare.  Thanks for the info ladies and gents. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap wid